Mechanical cantilever — 3D lattice with notch + rigid-arm ends
NonLinearStatic nmsteps 1 nsteps 1 contextOutputStep 1000 nmodules 2 profileopt 1 lstype 3 smtype 7
nsteps 10 rtolv 1.e-3 reqIterations 100 stiffMode 1 manrmsteps 10 maxiter 200 controllmode 1 minsteplength 1.e-10 maxrestarts 0 lstype 3 smtype 7
vtkxml primvars 1 1 tstep_all domain_all
gpexportmodule vars 5 59 90 84 85 78 tstep_all domain_all
domain 3dLattice
OutputManager tstep_all dofman_output { #@CTL2 }
ncrosssect 1 nmat 3 nbc 3 nic 0 nltf 2 nset 2
simplecs 1
latticedamage 1 talpha 0. d 0. e 30.e9 e0 100.e-6 stype 3 wf 40.e-6
latticedamage 2 talpha 0. d 0. e 30.e9 e0 1.e-6 stype 3 wf 40.e-6
